## Quick Audit Checklist

### Immediate Issues (Fix First):
- [ ] Headline clarity and relevance
- [ ] Page load speed under 1 second
- [ ] Single, obvious call-to-action
- [ ] Mobile responsiveness

### Conversion Optimization:
- [ ] Benefits vs features in copy
- [ ] Trust signals present
- [ ] Visual hierarchy guides eye flow
- [ ] Distractions removed

### Advanced Optimization:
- [ ] Audience language matching
- [ ] Emotional connection established
- [ ] Risk mitigation elements
- [ ] Professional visual design

## Success Metrics to Track:
- Conversion rate improvement
- Time on page
- Bounce rate reduction
- Form completion rates
- Mobile vs desktop performance